questions.quote: Okay. Would you rather live in the shirt pocket of a sweaty giant, or inside his shower drain?
Hey you guys, umm do either one of you want to get in there before I take my bath.
Oh no. I thought you said they could shoot the spot without you.
Uh, for your information, since they hired a very hot weather girl.
So anyway we really... Honey, we're just smoking all over you.
Oh no-no-no, not Dr. Burke. Dr. Burke is out of town. The-the on-call doctor will see me now.
This is ridiculous. I mean we had an agreement. Will you say something, Steven?! Please!!!
Okay, first of all, breathe. Second of all, I don't get it. Aren't you the one that decided that you didn't want to be with Ross?
For my last birthday you gave me a hug! Okay, read the card! Read the card!
Well, not for a little while. Let's just give him a few days to get used to everything else.
